title: BRIEF-Labcyte Reaches Agreement With Merck To Supply Acoustic-Mass Spectrometry Equipment
text:
April 17, 2018 / 11:33 AM / Updated 9 minutes ago BRIEF-Labcyte Reaches Agreement With Merck To Supply Acoustic-Mass Spectrometry Equipment Reuters Staff 
April 17 (Reuters) - Merck & Co Inc: 
* LABCYTE REACHES AGREEMENT WITH MERCK TO SUPPLY ACOUSTIC-MASS SPECTROMETRY EQUIPMENT 
* LABCYTE INC - AS PART OF AGREEMENT, PROTOTYPE ACOUSTIC-MS SYSTEMS WILL BE INSTALLED AT SELECT MERCK SITES Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
